    {
      "id": "https://www.silentorbit.com/static-online/blog/second",
      "url": "https://www.silentorbit.com/static-online/blog/second",
      "title": "Second post",
      "date_published": "2025-07-02 00:00:00+02:00",
      "content_html": "<p>Without inheriting the type BlogPost the following is needed to make it appear as a blog post:</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://www.silentorbit.com/static-online/post/2025-07-01/first_post",
      "url": "https://www.silentorbit.com/static-online/post/2025-07-01/first_post",
      "title": "First Post",
      "date_published": "2025-07-01 00:00:00+02:00",
      "date_modified": "2025-07-05 12:00:00+02:00",
      "content_html": "<p>By using <code>@inherits BlogPost</code> the page will be included in the list of <strong>posts and the feeds</strong>.</p>\n"
